casebody.data:
Edward S. WINEMAN, et al., petitioners,
v.
CITY OF SANTA MARIA, CALIFORNIA, et al. No. 12-1362. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, City of Santa Maria v. Adam, 211 Cal.App.4th 266 , 149 Cal.Rptr.3d 491 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the District Court of Appeal of California, Sixth Appellate District, denied. Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
